<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.7.8">
<l>paṭipulku maṭiyiṇai palartoḻa malarvaiku</l>
<l>koṭipulku taṭavarai yakalama tuṭaiyavar</l>
<l>muṭipulku neṭuvayal paṭaicela vaṭimalar</l>
<l>kaṭipulku kaṇapura maṭikaḷta miṭamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of god with a wide mountainous chest</l>
<l rend="indent">which embraces the creeper [lady]</l>
<l>Who dwells in a flower, as many worship both of his feet</l>
<l rend="indent">which embrace the earth,</l>
<l>Is Kaṇṇapuram, embraced by the fragrance of flowers which are struck,</l>
<l>As ploughs move in the long fields where clumps [of rice shoots] embrace.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
